    // bass → position, guitar 7/8 → 3nps, guitar 6 → caged); an advanced-mode
    // explicit pick wins. The shape-aware systems (caged/3nps/open) drive
    // fretMin/fretMax via the resolved shape; raw fretMin/fretMax inputs only
